               <msContents>
                  <summary>Psalter, ዳዊት፡ with Psalter of the Virgin; Praises of Mary, interwoven with Image of the Praises of Mary, መልክአ፡ ውዳሴ፡; Gate of Light, interwoven with Image of the Gate of Light, መልክዐ፡ አንቀጸ፡ ብርሃን፡; Asmat Prayer</summary>
